<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q25_v10" title="Q25_v10" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Se tiene la expresión 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mi>z</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>.
      Al aplicar la distributiva, un estudiante obtuvo
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mi>z</m:mi>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>6</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>.
      ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones muestra una forma correctamente simplificada de 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mi>z</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      a partir de
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mi>z</m:mi>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>6</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mi>z</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Desde 1 − 3z − 6 se agrupan los términos numéricos: 1 − 6 = −5. Por eso, una forma correctamente simplificada es (1 − 6) − 3z, que equivale a −5 − 3z.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mi>z</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión dada es 1 − 3z − 6. Los términos numéricos son 1 y −6, por lo que se debe calcular 1 − 6 = −5, no 1 + 6 = 7. Esta opción representa 7 − 3z, que no es equivalente a 1 − 3z − 6.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mi>z</m:mi>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si se desarrolla esta opción, resulta 1 − (3z − 6) = 1 − 3z + 6 = 7 − 3z. En cambio, la expresión original simplificada desde 1 − 3z − 6 es −5 − 3z. Como 7 − 3z y −5 − 3z son distintas, esta opción no corresponde.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mi>z</m:mi>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si se desarrolla esta opción, se obtiene 1 − 3(z − 2) = 1 − 3z + 6 = 7 − 3z. Pero desde 1 − 3z − 6, al reducir términos semejantes, se obtiene −5 − 3z. Por lo tanto, esta expresión no es equivalente a la original.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Simplificación paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Aplicar la distributiva</strong></p>
            <p>Partimos de:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Distribuyendo el −3 en el paréntesis:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Este resultado coincide con el que obtuvo el estudiante.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Identificar términos semejantes</strong></p>
            <p>En 
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>,
              los términos numéricos son 
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
              El término con variable es
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reducir los términos numéricos</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La opción A muestra:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Y como</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>,
            </p>
            <p>esa alternativa es equivalente a</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correctamente simplificada es</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>,
              que corresponde a la <strong>opción A</strong>.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>